{"tid":2436454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GD嫂熱戀早露餡！登《RM》抓包「貓耳朵狂動」羞曝戀情","createTime":"2021-03-07T07:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T07:38:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b93dd45110e905e5940416d450e181ec98e01b","tid":2436454,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:08:56.000Z","msg":"YG娛樂同門師兄妹G-Dragon與Jennie在上個月底被爆出熱戀，雖然公司仍以藝人私生活為由不多作解釋，但還是被外界挖出兩人各種戀愛的前兆，像是Jennie前陣子與BLACKPINK成員一同上《Running man》時，在被到感情問題的當下，雖鎮定的回應，但頭上的貓耳朵早狂動不已，如今看來果真事有蹊蹺，也間接應證了Jennie當時可能有戀愛的跡象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/07/2867961-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F07%2F2867961-PH.jpg&h=ae61a76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲睽違4年BLACKPINK再度登上《Running Man》。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK 微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/24/3038606-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F24%2F3038606-PH.jpg&h=b0a9bbf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK的成員Jennie被爆與師兄GD戀愛中。（圖／翻攝自jennierubyjane IG）<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK睽違4年重返《Running Man》，不只與主持人全昭旻合體大跳新歌，LiSA還在現場秀了一段招牌舞技「計程車舞」，更讓所有人直呼太可愛，但換主持人全昭旻模仿時，卻被虧說「你的計程車舞怎麼散發著酒精的味道？！」相同的音樂但跳起來卻整個大走鐘，相當搞笑，也讓舞蹈的原創者Lisa也笑到不行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/08/2598097-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F2598097-PH.jpg&h=05b68fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK成員Jennie的超甜撩人與Lisa大秀舞技成為節目看點。（圖／翻攝自Jennie IG）<br />\n<br />\n當遊戲進行到「用貓耳道具測謊」的環節時，測試者只要興奮或緊張，貓耳就會隨之擺動，當時就曾被李光洙問道：「有沒有感興趣的異性？」Jennie為自保於是直球反撩：「（光洙）哥哥！」讓李光洙招架不住超害羞，還被旁邊的隊友虧：「（光洙）別問這種問題，為了讓自己開心，太明顯了！」而Jennie也找機會反擊正在熱戀中的光洙：「是先彬姊姊漂亮，還是團員智秀比較漂亮？」此話一出反讓不只光洙緊張了起來，貓耳朵更是震動不已，也被其他主持人調侃：「在嘴巴回答前，大腦已先給出答案了。」，使現場笑聲不斷。"},{"pid":"589eb0a22a427f12c576876d314e775ee5c73ce2","tid":2436454,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"露你屎忽..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d93df75b337f8a001f296c507a15f675d42791","tid":2436454,"uid":70274,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"589eb0a22a427f12c576876d314e775ee5c73ce2","tid":2436454,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"露你屎忽..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXHJW8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXHJW8Z.png&h=835962b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25691d8b69dcba0f7930764fc8fec2c78123d843","tid":2436454,"uid":368454,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"死鯰魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n襯唔起我龍哥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b878f913bd44e46d0aa3e666f3707e683a783e29","tid":2436454,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"589eb0a22a427f12c576876d314e775ee5c73ce2","tid":2436454,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"露你屎忽..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"Shut the hell up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c684f3fbb7e794ae784739d85f5f819d96e58d","tid":2436454,"uid":93